# Health Blog Backend Integration

## Overview

Transform the Blog page into a fully functional health blog with search capabilities, backend integration, article management, and reading history tracking.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend - Database Schema

#### [NEW] [article.model.js](file:///c:/Users/makin/Desktop/health-navigator-pro/Backend/models/article.model.js)

Create Article schema with:
- **Basic Info**: title, slug, excerpt, content (rich text/markdown)
- **Metadata**: author, category, tags[], readTime, featured, published
- **SEO**: metaDescription, metaKeywords
- **Engagement**: views, likes
- **Timestamps**: createdAt, updatedAt, publishedAt

---

### Backend - Controllers

#### [NEW] [article.controller.js](file:///c:/Users/makin/Desktop/health-navigator-pro/Backend/controllers/article.controller.js)

Create controller functions:
- `getArticles`: Fetch articles with pagination, filtering, search
- `getArticleBySlug`: Get single article by slug
- `getFeaturedArticles`: Get featured articles
- `getArticlesByCategory`: Filter by category
- `searchArticles`: Full-text search across title, excerpt, content
- `incrementViews`: Track article views
- `likeArticle`: Like/unlike article

---

### Backend - Routes

#### [NEW] [article.route.js](file:///c:/Users/makin/Desktop/health-navigator-pro/Backend/routes/article.route.js)

Create routes:
- `GET /api/articles` - List articles (with query params for search, category, pagination)
- `GET /api/articles/featured` - Get featured articles
- `GET /api/articles/:slug` - Get article by slug
- `POST /api/articles/:id/view` - Increment view count
- `POST /api/articles/:id/like` - Like/unlike article

